Requirements
============

To compile pycddlib, you need Cython, which you can get from
http://www.cython.org/

Manual installation
===================

Windows
-------

On Windows you first need to set up your build environment, for
instance with MinGW:

http://www.mingw.org/
http://www.mingw.org/MinGWiki/index.php/Python extensions
http://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=2435&package_id=240780

Now, simply run

  python setup.py install --compiler=mingw32

Linux
-----

Simply run

  python setup.py install
